# 🧠 Pattern Recognition Cheat Codes

When you see:

| Clue in problem              | Think              |
| ---------------------------- | ------------------ |
| next greater/smaller         | monotonic stack    |
| nearest element              | stack              |
| histogram bars               | stack              |
| subarray minimum/maximum sum | contribution stack |
| sliding window max           | deque              |
| remove digits/letters        | greedy stack       |

